description: Experience coastal living within the city in this beautifully renovated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offering 1,002 square feet of thoughtfully designed space. The open-concept layout is ideal for modern living, featuring a stylishly updated kitchen that flows seamlessly into the living area. A cozy gas fireplace anchors the living room, creating the perfect spot to unwind or entertain. Step out from the kitchen onto a generous private deck, an ideal extension of the living space, perfect for dining alfresco. The large primary bedroom features peaceful water views and includes an ensuite bath with a stand up shower. A second bedroom and full bath offer flexibility for guests, a home office, or additional living space. With its smart updates, functional layout, and a great blend of indoor-outdoor living, this condo is move-in ready and ready for you to call it home!
